  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要设计一个库存管理系统的ER模型，核心是追踪物品（ITEM）在不同层级中的位置和归属关系。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ITEM"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，那ITEM需要关联到具体的实体（ENTITY）吗？比如公司、部门这种组织单元？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ITEM",
        "ENTITY"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，ITEM要belongs-to ENTITY。另外ENTITY本身也要有层级关系，比如子公司属于集团，用part-of来表达。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ITEM",
        "ENTITY",
        "belongs-to",
        "part-of"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出ENTITY和它的自引用关系part-of，以及ITEM到ENTITY的belongs-to关联。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ENTITY",
        "ITEM",
        "part-of",
        "belongs-to"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "接下来是LOCATION，物理位置。LOCATION也要belongs-to ENTITY，而且LOCATION本身可以嵌套，比如仓库里有库区、库区里有库位。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "LOCATION",
        "ENTITY",
        "belongs-to",
        "in-location"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "所以LOCATION有自引用的in-location关系，同时LOCATION到ENTITY是多对一的belongs-to？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "LOCATION",
        "ENTITY",
        "in-location",
        "belongs-to"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错。现在ITEM和LOCATION的关系比较复杂：ITEM有in-location表示存放位置，还要有current-location表示当前实际位置，这两个可能不同。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ITEM",
        "LOCATION",
        "in-location",
        "current-location"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加ITEM到LOCATION的两条关系线：in-location和current-location，都是多对一。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ITEM",
        "LOCATION",
        "in-location",
        "current-location"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
